{{Youmay|the [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] from the [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] continuity|[[Volo Bolus]]'s [[Spitfire|podracer]] of the same designation, from [[canon]]}}
[[File:Spitfire_es.jpg|thumb|right|250px|''Spitfire'' under attack from an Imperial [[TIE/ad starfighter|TIE Avenger]].]]
[[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Delta-class JV-7 escort shuttle|''Delta''-class JV-7 escort shuttle]] '''''Spitfire''''' served in the Rebel fleet during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. ''Spitfire'' escorted [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] [[Triumph (corvette group)|''Triumph'']] during the [[Treachery at Ottega]]. Shuttle ''Spitfire'' futilely attacked Imperial [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] in attempt to save [[MC40a light cruiser/Legends|MC40a light cruiser]] [[Warhawk (MC40a light cruiser)|''Warhawk'']] and defecting [[Victory-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Victory-class Star Destroyer]] [[Protector (Victory I-class)|''Protector'']], only to be destroyed.

